        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
            <head>Scope and Content </head>
            <p>Petition of Mary Batts, executrix for her husband, John Batts, deceased, to George
                Wythe, judge of the chancery court, Richmond {Va.}. Concerns repayment of her
                husband's debt to Benjamin Putney, and devaluation of currency following the
                Revolution. Includes note in George Wythe's hand. </p>
        </scopecontent>
